maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: Did human really bring \c[3]black monster\c[0] into village?
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Est-ce que humain avoir vraiment apporté \c[3]monstre noir\c[0] dans village ?

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: Didn't you hear about \c[3]source\c[0] of black monster? It very shiny and metal!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Toi pas avoir entendu parler de \c[3]source\c[0] de monstre noir ? Être très brillant et métallique !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: But we never saw human bring monsters or source into village!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Mais nous avoir jamais vu humain apporter monstre ou source dans village !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: That true, but who else could done it?
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Ça vrai, mais qui d'autre pouvoir faire ça ?

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: I can not trade with you human. Humans have made jungle sick.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Je peux pas marchander avec humains. Humains avoir rendu jungle malade.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: You may helped Shad, but I still not trust human!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Vous peut-être avoir aidé Shad, mais moi toujours pas faire confiance à humain !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: I saw you getting rid of the \v[combat.name.minibosses/shockcat-black]s from here, thanks for that!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Je vous ai vu d'ici vous débarrasser des \v[combat.name.minibosses/shockcat-black]s, merci pour ça !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: Good. And it looks as sturdy as ever.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Bien. Et elle a l'air toujours aussi solide.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: Now we can sneak past the guards.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Maintenant nous pouvons nous faufiler à travers les gardes.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: But we have to take a \c[3]little detour first\c[0].
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Mais il faut faire un \c[3]petit détour en premier\c[0].

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: The hidden path we need to use is outside the village.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Le chemin caché que nous devons utiliser est en dehors du village.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: Following the \c[3]right path\c[0] to the Grand Krys'kajo at \c[3]Clinging River\c[0] there's a small tree.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: En suivant le \c[3]bon chemin\c[0] vers le \v[area.tree-dng.name] à la \c[3]Rivière Stagnante\c[0], il y a un petit arbre.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: Seeker helped us get rid of cats.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: \v[lore.title.seeker] avoir aidé à débarrasser des chats.
Humains pas tous mauvais, toi voir ?

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: Maybe not reason for \c[3]black monsters\c[0] after all!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Peut-être humains pas être raison pour \c[3]monstre noirs\c[0] en fait !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: These Shads are experts in wooden constructions.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Ces Shads sont des experts des constructions en bois.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.orig: Even with the fierce weather of the jungle, these bridges are said to remain stable for many years.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-02.json/.text: Malgré la météo rude de la jungle, on dit de ces ponts qu'ils peuvent rester debout pendant plusieurs années.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: K'tara house is now lost thanks to \c[3]black monsters\c[0].
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Maison de K'tara est perdue à cause de \c[3]monstre noirs\c[0].

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Eldress not happy.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Altesse pas contente.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: You helped with black creatures, thank you Human.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Vous avoir aidé avec créatures noires, merci Humain.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Humans really that bad?
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Humain vraiment si méchant ?

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Yes! Probably infested jungle on purpose.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Oui ! Probablement avoir infecté jungle volontairement.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: They want to take our land!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Eux vouloir prendre nos terres !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Not sure if true...
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Pas sûr si vrai...

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: K'tara
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: K'tara

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Find the \c[3]Stone Key\c[0] inside my house and bring it here.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Trouvez la \c[3]\v[item.427.name]\c[0] dans ma maison et apportez-là ici.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Once you got it, let's meet again at the \c[3]V'rda Vil landmark\c[0]!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Une fois que vous l'aurez, rencontrons-nous au \c[3]point de repère de V'rda Vil\c[0]

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: K'tara
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: K'tara

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Hello again!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Bonjour, encore !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Hi...
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Salut...

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: This is the northern part of the village.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: C'est la partie nord du village.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: As you can see, the beasts have already come this far.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Comme vous pouvez le voir, les bestioles sont déjà arrivées jusqu'ici.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: K'tara
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: K'tara

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: These are the black cats that have taken over our village.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Ce sont ces chats noirs qui ont envahi notre village.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: We call them \c[3]Wiccats\c[0].
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: On les appelle des \c[3]\v[combat.name.minibosses/shockcat-black]s\c[0].

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: But these are only a few. The real threat is further ahead in the \c[3]Chief's Den\c[0].
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Mais ils sont peu nombreux. La vraie menace se trouve plus loin dans la \c[3]Hutte du Chef\c[0].

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: K'tara
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: K'tara

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: However, there is no way the other Shad will let you through.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Mais, les autres Shads ne vous laisseront jamais passer.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: The villagers are dead set on shutting down the power plant. They will deny any other kind of outside help.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Les villageois sont déterminés pour faire fermer la centrale. Ils refusent toute aide extérieure.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Yes, I know it's cumbersome. It's the same kind of stubbornness I know from a certain someone...
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Oui, je sais, c'est agaçant. Ils sont aussi bornés qu'une certaine autre personne...

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Anyway, that means we have to help them... in a sneaky way. And I have a plan.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: En tout cas, il faut que nous les aidions... discrètement. Et je sais déjà comment.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: You see that house over there?
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Tu vois la maison là-bas ?

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: K'tara
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: K'tara

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: That is my home. It's now overrun by those creatures, but it has a valuable treasure!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: C'est ma maison. Elle est maintenant assiégée par ces créatures, mais elle abrite un trésor précieux !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: One that lets us sneak our way around the guards.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Un qui va nous permettre de passer outre les gardes.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: All we need to do is get it. That's where you come in.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: On doit juste le récupérer. C'est là que vous entrez en jeu.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: K'tara
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: K'tara

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: You need to go into my house and grab my old \c[3]Stone Key\c[0].
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Vous devez aller dans ma maison et piquer ma vielle \c[3]\v[item.427.name]\c[0].

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Do you think you can do that?
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Vous pensez que vous pouvez faire ça ?

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Great!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Super !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: I leave it up to you if you want to get rid of the cats or not.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Je vous laisse le choix si vous voulez vous débarrasser des chats ou pas.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: The more are gone, the happier everyone will be I imagine.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Moins il y en aura, plus tout le monde sera content, c'est ce que je me dis.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: But they are very aggressive so be careful!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Mais ils sont très agressifs donc soyez prudent !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Okay, let's open these ropes so you can jump down from here.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: OK, ouvrons un passage à travers ces cordes pour que vous puissiez sauter en bas.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Sadly, there is no other way in...
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Malheureusement, il n'y a pas d'autres chemins...

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: K'tara
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: K'tara

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Alright, that did the trick.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Bon, ça a marché.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Once you've got the key, let's meet again at the \c[3]V'rda Vil landmark\c[0]!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Une fois que vous aurez la clef, rencontrons-nous à nouveau au \c[3]point de repère de V'rda Vil\c[0] !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Good luck and may the Krys'kajo be with you.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Bonne chance et que le Krys'kajo soit avec vous.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: So... we only have to get the key.\. We don't have to fight those kittens, right?
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Donc... on a juste besoin de récupérer la clé.\. On a pas besoin de combattre ces chatons, hein ?

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: We don't have to.\. Still, those Wiccats are a true threat to those villagers!
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: On en n'a pas besoin.\. Mais, ces \v[combat.name.minibosses/shockcat-black]s sont une véritable menace pour ces villageois !

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Aww.\. They're so cute, though.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Ohhh, mais ils sont si mignons.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Sonya Bolt
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Sonya Foudre

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: The Terror of Man can truly reside in the most innocent places and corrupt them.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: La terreur de l'Homme ne peut se nicher que dans les endroits les plus innocents et les corrompre.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: ...why?
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: ... pourquoi ?

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Just look, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. Even directly next to a village of the unsuspecting Shad those creatures run rampant.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Regarde, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. Même à côté d'un village de Shads qui ignorent ce qui se passe, ces créatures grouillent.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: That location device even suggests that the facility itself is near.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Cet appareil de localisation suggère même que l'installation elle-même est toute proche.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: ...Lea?
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: ... Lea ?

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Yes, \v[lore.title.seeker], the facility that created those dangerous beings.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Oui, \v[lore.title.seeker], l'installation qui a créé ces êtres dangereux.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: You have to find it and uncover its secrets, so the machinations of the powerful can be stopped in the future.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Vous devez la trouver et découvrir ses secrets, pour que cette machination des puissants puisse être stoppée.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Good... Very good.\. Now, go.\. And be careful.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Bien... Très bien.\. Maintenant partez, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. Et soyez prudent.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.orig: Bye.
maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Bye.

maps/jungle/clearing/clear-path-03.json/.text: Clef Appliquée
